肖恩·麦克高恩 (Shane MacGowan) 接受重症监护后康复https://www.nme.com/news/music/shane-macgowan-recovering-after-stay-in-intense-care-3472135?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=shane-macgowan-recovering-after-stay-in-intense-careEmma Wilkes Sun, 23 Jul 2023 09:51:15 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3472135 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肖恩·麦克高恩 2016 年" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他的妻子说：“他仍在医院，但情况良好并得到照顾。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shane-macgowan-recovering-after-stay-in-intensive-care-3472135">肖恩·麦克高恩 (Shane MacGowan) 在重症监护室康复后的康复情况</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肖恩·麦克高恩 2016 年" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Shane-macGowan-2016-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-pogues">波格斯队</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shane-macgowan">肖恩·麦高恩</a>被送进重症监护室后正在医院康复。</p><p>他的妻子维多利亚·玛丽·克拉克证实，这位音乐家因不明健康问题在重症监护室住了几天。据了解，他自六月底以来一直住在都柏林的医院里。</p><p> “他仍在医院，但情况良好，并得到照顾，”她告诉<em>《爱尔兰星期日镜报》</em> 。我不想让人们担心。他已经出重症监护室，情况良好。” [来自<em><a href="https://www.dublinlive.ie/news/celebs/pogues-frontman-shane-macgowan-recovers-27377239" target="_blank" rel="noopener">都柏林直播</a></em>]</p><p>克拉克上个月在 Instagram 上发布的一篇帖子中评论了麦高恩的健康恐慌，并在帖子中标记了麦高恩的账户。</p><p> “最近我的生活发生了很多动荡，非常情绪化，也很可怕，”她写道。</p><p> “但在过去的几天里，我注意到，尽管有很多恐惧，但也有大量的爱和支持以及令人难以置信的祝福。我认为我们的思想非常抗拒改变，抗拒我们的生活被动摇和重新安排，我们需要对自己非常温柔和耐心......</p><p> “保持当下的感受是一个挑战。感谢所有支持我和@shanemacgowanofficial 的人。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Ct_Y1fhMVRJ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.